                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If &quot;./configure&quot; script is used with &quot;--disable-tests&quot; option the rpms are not produced.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;RPM build errors:&lt;br/&gt;
    File not found: /home/rpmbuild/BUILDROOT/lustre-client-2.4.93-2.6.32_358.18.1.el6_lustre.g02a976b.x86_64_g26c55b2.x86_64/usr/bin/mcreate&lt;br/&gt;
