make: *** &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;rpms&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; Error 1&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This was introduced by fix for &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3466&quot; title=&quot;Make lustre-iokit a subpackage of lustre&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3466&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3466&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; commit a0a1066d30054540d853a067449b90f991b7554a when wildcard was replaced by list of files.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
